  </picture>

</div>
      
</div>
</div>
      
                        
                            <div class="summary"><div class="view view-summary view-id-summary view-display-id-meta_summary js-view-dom-id-6793fb1774829a3e246970ce36249c66a65712a93e89e5012dbf53b21a57b9eb">
  
    
      
      <div class="view-content">
          <div class="views-row"><p>CBO analyzes 36 policy options commonly proposed by policymakers and analysts. Most of them would improve Social Security’s long-term finances, but only a few would significantly postpone the combined trust funds’ exhaustion date.
</p></div>

    </div>
  
          </div>

</div>
            
